  "page": "Observations Upon the Recent Blood-Letting on the Stepstones",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><i><b>Observations Upon the Recent Blood-Letting on the Stepstones</b></i> is, according to a semi-canon source, a text about the <a href=\"/index.php/War_of_the_Ninepenny_Kings\" title=\"War of the Ninepenny Kings\">War of the Ninepenny Kings</a> by Grand Maester <a href=\"/index.php/Pycelle\" title=\"Pycelle\">Pycelle</a>. In the work Pycelle praises the deeds of Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Tywin_Lannister\" title=\"Tywin Lannister\">Tywin Lannister</a> and his brothers, Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Kevan_Lannister\" title=\"Kevan Lannister\">Kevan</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Tygett_Lannister\" title=\"Tygett Lannister\">Tygett</a>, during the campaign in the <a href=\"/index.php/Stepstones\" title=\"Stepstones\">Stepstones</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-sample_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-sample-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Quotes\">Quotes</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Observations_Upon_the_Recent_Blood-Letting_on_the_Stepstones&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Quotes\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p>Those who beheld <a href=\"/index.php/House_Lannister\" title=\"House Lannister\">these proud young lions</a> on the battlefield might rightly wonder how such could ever have sprung from the loins of <a href=\"/index.php/Tytos_Lannister\" title=\"Tytos Lannister\">the quivering fool</a> beneath <a href=\"/index.php/Casterly_Rock\" title=\"Casterly Rock\">the Rock</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-sample_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-sample-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;writings of <a href=\"/index.php/Pycelle\" title=\"Pycelle\">Pycelle</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Observations_Upon_the_Recent_Blood-Letting_on_the_Stepstones&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-sample-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-sample_1-0\">1.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-sample_1-1\">1.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i>: The Westerlands (unabridged). <a class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.georgerrmartin.com/world-of-ice-and-fire-sample/\">georgerrmartin.com</a></span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260403134905\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.015 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.035 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 60/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 301/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 648/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 302/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 3/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 648/5000000 bytes\nLua time usage: 0.010/7.000 seconds\nLua virtual size: 4.51 MB/50 MB\nLua estimated memory usage: 0 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%   30.877      1 -total\n 88.87%   27.441      1 Template:Italic_title\n  5.06%    1.563      1 Template:References\n  3.26%    1.006      1 Template:Quote\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache 